PERFORMANCE EVALUATION:

confusion matrix:
tp fn
fp tn

actual 
1-1 true
1-0-negative
0-0- true
0-1 false

accuracy = 
tp+tn / tp+fn+fp+tn

precision and recall are use to information retrival

precision will be TP/TP+FP
tp- true positive 
tp+fp - acutual positive values
in case to find negative change positive into negative

recall- 
TP/P
tp- true positive 
p- total positive

implent using sklearn lib
comment - classification_report
(Y_test,Y_prediction) =  1 0
1 -- 0 will be convert into percentage

f1 score = s* presion*recall / precision+recall
over all value need 1 is good model

